OL,3,CMiddlesbrough on standby for return to
OL,4,Ctraining as 'Spygate' hearing begins
OL,6,FMiddlesbrough's players are on standby
OL,7,Fto return to training later this week
OL,8,Fpending the outcome of the 'Spygate'
OL,9,Fhearing.
OL,11,FAn independent commission will hear
OL,12,Fcharges lodged by the EFL against
OL,13,FSouthampton on Tuesday (19 May) in
OL,14,Frelation to allegations a member of
OL,15,Ftheir staff spied on a Boro training
OL,16,Fsession on 7 May, ahead of the sides'
OL,17,FChampionship play-off semi-final first
OL,18,Fleg.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
