FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1779732663
OL,3,CMiddlesbrough on standby for return to
OL,4,Ctraining as 'Spygate' hearing begins
OL,6,FMiddlesbrough have publicly called for
OL,7,Fthe Saints to be thrown out of
OL,8,FSaturday's play-off final at Wembley,
OL,9,Fwhere they are scheduled to face Hull.
OL,11,FIf the commission did expel
OL,12,FSouthampton, Boro would immediately
OL,13,Fresume training. The Press Association
OL,14,Funderstands players did not attend
OL,15,Ftheir Rockliffe Park headquarters on
OL,16,FTuesday but will report in on
OL,17,FWednesday.
OL,19,FWhether they train then or not, or for
OL,20,Fthe rest of the week, depends entirely
OL,21,Fon the hearing outcome.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
