OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1779732663
OL,3,CMiddlesbrough on standby for return to
OL,4,Ctraining as 'Spygate' hearing begins
OL,6,FThe timescales for the commission are
OL,7,Ftight. If either Southampton or the
OL,8,FEFL wish to appeal against the
OL,9,Foutcome, there is precious little time
OL,10,Fto convene a second hearing and reach
OL,11,Fa further verdict before Saturday.
OL,13,FThe EFL has acknowledged the
OL,14,Fpossibility Saturday's match is
OL,15,Ftherefore subject to change. The EFL
OL,16,Fsaid last week it had "a number of
OL,17,Fcontingency plans" in place depending
OL,18,Fon the outcome of the legal
OL,19,Fproceedings.
OL,26,@xD@WOUyD@RO]
