OL,3,CMiddlesbrough on standby for return to
OL,4,Ctraining as 'Spygate' hearing begins
OL,6,FTickets went on sale to Southampton
OL,7,Fand Hull fans last Friday morning.
OL,9,FLast week, Middlesbrough said a
OL,10,Fsporting sanction which would prevent
OL,11,FSouthampton playing in the play-off
OL,12,Ffinal was the "only appropriate
OL,13,Fresponse".
OL,15,FThe club had sought to be a party in
OL,16,Fthe commission hearing but was denied
OL,17,Fthe opportunity.
